cdata.name: Kucoin
cdata.desc:
KCS is an Ethereum-based ERC20 token issued by theKucoin Cryptocurrency Exchange. The token holders benefit from bonuses (50% of the total trading fees charged by the platform), trading fee discounts, and otherspecial services.

KucoinCryptocurrency Exchange will buy back 100 million of the 200 million total tokens issued and burned them.
